snippet.title: Longplay of Sonic Riders: Zero Gravity
snippet.description:
Longplay of Sonic Riders: Zero Gravity, played as the PAL version on the PlayStation 2. This game's version was released on Feb. 22nd, 2008. Tell us what you think by leaving a comment down below!

0:00:00 - Opening
0:04:40 - Beginner's Course (last part missing due to a recording  error)
0:08:30 - Hands on Course (first part missing due to recording error)
0:14:59 - Heroes Story Start
0:17:49 - Stage 1
0:23:06 - Stage 2
0:30:08 - Stage 3
0:38:50 - Stage 4
0:45:19 - Stage 5
0:54:44 - Stage 6
0:59:07 - Heroes Story Ending and Credits
1:05:30 - Babylon Story Start
1:08:39 - Stage 1
1:14:55 - Stage 2
1:20:57 - Stage 3
1:26:54 - Stage 4
1:33:37 - Stage 5
1:42:09 - Stage 6
1:50:18 - Final Boss
1:55:26 - Babylon Story Ending and Credits

By: nikodem123asdf
